== Notes

For the CAPTCHA to work, in all pages there must be a div that the id
"container" and contains all elements.

== Tip: Fix for IE

The right div drops down on IE if the font is justify and italic at the same
time. If justify is used, the following fix is needed:

/* Fix IE: the right div drops down if font is justify and italic at the same time */
blockquote {
  font-style: normal;
  padding-left: 10px;
  border-left: 4px solid #B9335D;
}

/* Fix IE: the right div drops down if font is justify and italic at the same time */
em {
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: bolder;
}

== Tip: Fix for Blueprint

/* Fix Blueprint: clear float:left for images */
#container img {
  float: none;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}
